<header class="large-header">
	<h2 class="page-name">Widgets</h2>
</header>

<main class="content" tabindex="-1">
	<section class="text">
		<img class="widget-demo" src="images/widget_demo.png" />

		<p>
			Widgets have their own settings and can't be customized here.
			<br /><br />
			To edit a widget's settings, follow these steps:
		</p>

		<ol>
			<li>Move your mouse over any widget</li>
			<li>Click the wrench icon that appears at the top right of the widget. If none appears then this widget doesn't have any settings that can be customized.</li>
			<li>Edit any of the settings shown</li>
			<li>Click Save to save your changes, or any part of the background to get rid of them</li>
		</ol>
	</section>
</main>